snippet.textDisplay:
If someone wants to learn how a mureed (follower) should respect and love his peer (master)...............just listen to the kalams of Hazrat Ameer Khusro (R.A). 
In rang / rung; performed by Fareed Ayaz & Abu Muhammad and Amjad Sabri & Rahat Fateh Ali.....you will see what happens when a person meets a Wali / Sufi Saint for the first time......... how it transforms his life and what is that experience, what a trans and what a transformation.

Then this kalam..........which expresses the follower's extreme respect and his high regard for his master saint. His utmost faithfulness, his devotion to his master (in sufisim it is called fana fi sheikh and is a first step towards the ultimate objective of fana fi ALLAH)......... when he expresses that even if you don't look at me, even if you don't talk to me ........ I wont be leaving your side...........I will be with you forever........and look his eternal place is with his master at Dehli...... as if his wishes and prayers were answered by ALLAH(s.w.t).
